---
// Shared between the homepage and the OG preview page (card-preview/index.astro)
---

<div class="home-header">
  <p class="label">aesthetic.fyi</p>
  <h1>Every web aesthetic,<br />demonstrated.</h1>
  <p class="desc">A visual reference for web design aesthetics. Each page is designed in the style it describes.</p>
</div>

<style>
  .home-header {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: #eee;
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #888;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .desc {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #777;
    font-weight: 400;
    max-width: 500px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
